Enclosing class:
HandlerStateMachine
 class HandlerStateMachine.SmHandler
extends Handler

Handle messages sent to the state machine by calling the current state's processMessage. It also handles the enter/exit calls and placing any deferred messages back onto the queue when transitioning to a new state.
